---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
import PageHeader from '../components/PageHeader.astro';
import todo100 from '../data/todo100.json';

interface TodoItem {
  order: number;
  text: string;
  subText?: string;
  done: boolean;
  inProgress?: boolean;
}

const items = todo100.items as TodoItem[];
---

<Base title="About me" summary="Hej! I'm Đào Đức Cương (a.k.a. Erik), welcome to my blog! I'm a software engineer and machine learning lover with five+ years of experience. I'm super excited to share with you what I've learned in this blog." socialImage="/images/about/fb_og_about.png">
  <PageHeader title="About me" summary="Hej! I'm Đào Đức Cương (a.k.a. Erik), welcome to my blog! I'm a software engineer and machine learning lover with five+ years of experience. I'm super excited to share with you what I've learned in this blog." />

  <div class="flex flex-col text-xl font-light mb-16">
    <article class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-light leading-snug mb-4 space-y-4">
      <p>I start this blog with two purposes 1) to document my journey while learning new things, and 2) to share them with others and my future self. The former reason is to make sure that I understand what I've learned, and also to eliminate my scare of writing ;-) And the latter is to satisfy my wish to contribute to the community. I like to learn new things, and as I'm learning, this blog is always a work-in-progress. That's said, there might be something you disagree with or want to give your comments about on this blog, and you're more than welcome to do so. Let's talk!</p>
    </article>

    <article class="flex flex-col mb-8" id="louis">
      <h2 class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-medium mb-4">
        <a href="#louis">
          <span class="text-bach-orange-600 border-b-4 border-bach-orange-100 pb-0.5 hover:bg-bach-orange-100 cursor-pointer">Louis - The cat</span>
        </a>
      </h2>
      <p>In May 2018, I welcomed Louis - a British shorthair - to my home. We lived together for three years in various places. Sadly, I couldn't bring him with me when I moved to Sweden. He's forstered by a friend and has been enjoying his new home with another cat named Tei Tei. As of September 2021, Louis is the father of 5 cute kittens.</p>

      <div class="flex p-4 mt-4">
        <ul role="list" class="grid grid-cols-2 sm:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
          <li>
            <div class="flex flex-col">
              <img src="/images/about/louis-0.jpg" alt="Louis 0" class="rounded-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow duration-100">
            </div>
          </li>
          <li>
            <div class="flex flex-col">
              <img src="/images/about/louis-1.jpg" alt="Louis 1" class="rounded-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow duration-100">
            </div>
          </li>
          <li>
            <div class="flex flex-col">
              <img src="/images/about/louis-2.jpg" alt="Louis 2" class="rounded-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow duration-100">
            </div>
          </li>
          <li>
            <div class="flex flex-col">
              <img src="/images/about/louis-3.jpg" alt="Louis 3" class="rounded-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow duration-100">
            </div>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </article>

    <article class="flex flex-col" id="list-100">
      <h2 class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-medium mb-4">
        <a href="#list-100">
          <span class="text-bach-orange-600 border-b-4 border-bach-orange-100 pb-0.5 hover:bg-bach-orange-100 cursor-pointer">100 things I want to do while I am alive</span>
        </a>
      </h2>
      <ul>
        {items.map((item) => (
          <li class="leading-snug flex items-center">
            {item.done ? (
              <span class="text-green-400 w-8">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                </svg>
              </span>
            ) : item.inProgress ? (
              <span class="text-blue-500 w-8">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
                  <path d="M6 10a1.5 1.5 0 11-3 0 1.5 1.5 0 013 0zm5.5 0a1.5 1.5 0 11-3 0 1.5 1.5 0 013 0zM15.5 11.5a1.5 1.5 0 100-3 1.5 1.5 0 000 3z" />
                </svg>
              </span>
            ) : (
              <span class="w-8 block flex-shrink-0">&nbsp;</span>
            )}
            <span class="inline-block w-8">{item.order}.</span>
            <span>{item.text}</span>
            {item.subText && <span class="ml-1 text-base text-gray-600">{item.subText}</span>}
          </li>
        ))}
      </ul>
    </article>
  </div>
</Base>
